fr.ign.cogit.geoxygene.util.graphcut

Class GraphCut

  • Object
    • GraphCut

  • public class GraphCut
extends Object
    Author:
    JeT Algorithm used to paste tiles into an image using the graph-cut algorithm It stores a mask image to know where previous tiles have been pasted. The algorithm computes a connected cut between existing image and tile which has the minimal perceptible difference This class alters the given image, it does not copy it !
